{"tid":423014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸版鹹蛋超人正式上映　日本圓谷表示將提訴","createTime":"2017-10-03T14:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T07:04:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5d15827cca6304082ab14af4f55db49138e9eb","tid":423014,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru001-694x386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru001-694x386.jpg&h=1631ce03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事先張揚會在10月1日大陸國慶節首映，大陸版鹹蛋超人的《鋼鐵飛龍之再見奧特曼》，果然前日在大陸戲院正式上畫。而日本方面的原作擁有者圓谷製作公司，據報會正式展開法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n製作單位聲稱得到正式授權，不過電影中出場的 Ultraman 鹹蛋超人有 6 塊腹肌，全身佈滿灰線，而且在宣傳活動上出現的鹹蛋超人，更出現超古怪的下顎，突出乳首的情況，被日本當地網民批評質素太低。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本傳媒 ITMedia 向原作人圓谷製作室的查詢，目前他們已經確認有關影片已經上映。圓谷曾經向製作單位數次發出警告書，還有已經為製作發表會等侵權行為作出起訴。今次令到日本以至全世界的鹹蛋超人推躉都非常擔心事件，他們致以最大的歉意。而這次電影的正式上映，他們將會對侵權行為展開法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n《鋼鐵飛龍之再見奧特曼》的製作單位廣州藍弧文化傳播有限公司以及樂視影業，稱從一間名為「UM Corporation Co. Ltd.」的公司買入的權利，是在 1976 年得到圓谷的正式授權書，當中提到該公司可在日本以外的全球地區無限期享有「奧特曼」（Ultraman）的製作權、版權、商標權。而圓谷則指泰國法庭已經在 2008 年裁判 1976 年的合同是偽造品，涉案泰國人並已被判有罪，他們透過上海的合作公司發出聲明，指電影製作者提出的理據與事實大相徑庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru002-694x386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru002-694x386.jpg&h=3ff97af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg&h=4085f6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/94faqivh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F94faqivh&h=180542a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DESub22Q-Zq0%26t%3D1s&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a475cd74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2Ffakeultraman%2Fhottopic%2F&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0a62fb42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/</a>"},{"pid":"8d50c9f2ce7b9b8c9175ebdbbe80ff498f86f830","tid":423014,"uid":21907,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"個下巴係咪武器之一"},{"pid":"41e026db3722add2e53cd40013d234c6bbc0730b","tid":423014,"uid":521,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"無 恥 無 極 限"},{"pid":"dbb7c90b12f913da42bab7f8a678bbee26bf6ae7","tid":423014,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"轉頭話 ultraman 係中國創造，告返轉頭"},{"pid":"8273caebbb552b49c2919355f488f653a058c39f","tid":423014,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個下巴係咪武器之一</blockquote><br />\n可以當回力標咁用"},{"pid":"bf2594a24dafbb5f037dfda7e64c4f36a50bb358","tid":423014,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個下巴係咪武器之一</blockquote><br />\n可以當回力標咁用</blockquote><br />\n整容失敗姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9622973591dc08691d5fbea01a1b60636aabc00","tid":423014,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03c9e309ee3217b919ae499fc00a4ec1f4700b62","tid":423014,"uid":33756