=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru002-694x386.jpg&h=3ff97af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg&h=4085f6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/94faqivh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F94faqivh&h=180542a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DESub22Q-Zq0%26t%3D1s&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a475cd74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2Ffakeultraman%2Fhottopic%2F&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0a62fb42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />last 嗰張唔係香港黎掛  好瘀</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中環匯豐銀行"},{"pid":"2a13c0c8f56761d7dd59379d10c45d53ebea1ea3","tid":423014,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"支那MAN"},{"pid":"5883696ae7b9f5e023bf5bd2c206fd31eed2134b","tid":423014,"uid":79672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru001-694x386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru001-694x386.jpg&h=1631ce03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事先張揚會在10月1日大陸國慶節首映，大陸版鹹蛋超人的《鋼鐵飛龍之再見奧特曼》，果然前日在大陸戲院正式上畫。而日本方面的原作擁有者圓谷製作公司，據報會正式展開法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n製作單位聲稱得到正式授權，不過電影中出場的 Ultraman 鹹蛋超人有 6 塊腹肌，全身佈滿灰線，而且在宣傳活動上出現的鹹蛋超人，更出現超古怪的下顎，突出乳首的情況，被日本當地網民批評質素太低。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本傳媒 ITMedia 向原作人圓谷製作室的查詢，目前他們已經確認有關影片已經上映。圓谷曾經向製作單位數次發出警告書，還有已經為製作發表會等侵權行為作出起訴。今次令到日本以至全世界的鹹蛋超人推躉都非常擔心事件，他們致以最大的歉意。而這次電影的正式上映，他們將會對侵權行為展開法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n《鋼鐵飛龍之再見奧特曼》的製作單位廣州藍弧文化傳播有限公司以及樂視影業，稱從一間名為「UM Corporation Co. Ltd.」的公司買入的權利，是在 1976 年得到圓谷的正式授權書，當中提到該公司可在日本以外的全球地區無限期享有「奧特曼」（Ultraman）的製作權、版權、商標權。而圓谷則指泰國法庭已經在 2008 年裁判 1976 年的合同是偽造品，涉案泰國人並已被判有罪，他們透過上海的合作公司發出聲明，指電影製作者提出的理據與事實大相徑庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru002-694x386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru002-694x386.jpg&h=3ff97af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/l_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fl_kikka_171002uru003-694x390.jpg&h=4085f6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/94faqivh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F94faqivh&h=180542a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DESub22Q-Zq0%26t%3D1s&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a475cd74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESub22Q-Zq0&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2Ffakeultraman%2Fhottopic%2F&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0a62fb42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/03/fakeultraman/hottopic/</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />last 嗰張唔係香港黎掛  好瘀</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中環匯豐銀行</blockquote><br />\n條片有好多係max埋<br />\n香港果度係cosplay<br />\n太郎,老豆老母玩yoga結婚果兩段直頭係官方宣傳片黎<br />\n最搞笑係一開波出變身畫面果個係阿鄉黎,之後先加插返吉田<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac3c9a5067bc6b68bdf0ae83f6c6c37607df2d7","tid":423014,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"等軍日本仔比人告番轉頭"},{"pid":"55798069ca4a769d2bed7082fb7ec91377b308b0","tid":423014,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個下巴係咪武器之一</blockquote><br />\n學園handsome <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a790a30e0f48861e70f476cd5d5fd491a8d0cf","tid":423014,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"屌你咩 仲要黎香港取境"},{"pid":"634b03d5ecd59440cab5b2ee8ab2692574bfbf3b","tid":423014,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"支那狗不意外"},{"pid":"837ce3d019c97d93be107a7f5d8d548c4a5b0c45","tid":423014,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"我睇緊乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後有transformer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c596f783878987763d3fd52f6ae215f1d069db04","tid":423014,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef5bf460474181989fc30e11ffa87